@startuml
title AI Governance Workflow (Sequence UML)

actor User
participant "Assistant UI" as UI
participant "Assistant Orchestrator" as Orchestrator
participant "Grounding Guard" as Guard
participant "Read Adapter" as Reader
database "Internal Asset Data" as Data
participant "Approval Service (Human)" as Approval
participant "Audit Emitter" as Audit

User -> UI : Ask natural-language question
UI -> Orchestrator : Submit intent
Orchestrator -> Guard : Validate scope (internal-only)
Guard -> Reader : Read-only query plan
Reader -> Data : Execute query (read-only)
Data --> Reader : Results
Reader --> Orchestrator : Evidence package

alt Sufficient data
  Orchestrator --> UI : Answer + provenance + correlation_id
else Insufficient data
  Orchestrator --> UI : insufficient_data + clarifying questions
end

Orchestrator -> Audit : Append immutable recommendation event

== High-impact action path ==
User -> Approval : Request override/approval
Approval -> Audit : Record decision, actor, rationale, timestamp
note right of Approval
Dual-control required for
high-impact overrides.
end note
@enduml

